<section xml:id="mongo.trouble" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
 <title>Troubleshooting</title>

 <para>
  If you're having trouble, there are lots of resources you can turn to.
 </para>

 <itemizedlist>
  <listitem>
   <para>IRC</para>
   <para>
    The official MongoDB IRC room is irc.freenode.net/#mongodb.  This is the
    fastest way to get help... if there are people around.
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>Mailing List</para>
   <para>
    <link xlink:href="groups.google.com/group/mongodb-user/">MongoDB's mailing list</link>
    is a good (and usually very fast) way to get answers to questions. 
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>Bug Tracker</para>
   <para>
    Found a bug?  Want a feature?  Have a question?  File it in the 
    <link xlink:href="http://jira.mongodb.org/browse/PHP">PHP driver's bug tracker</link>.
   </para>
  </listitem>
 </itemizedlist>

</section>

